{"tid":2185343,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[肚痛撚] 有無巴打絲打一食野就好易肚痛+肚屙?","createTime":"2020-09-02T07:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T12:26:02.000Z","uid":227967,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f7cc7cfa20f3980ec15eb17c6129fc5d2a16d791","tid":2185343,"uid":227967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"平時腸胃唔算係好好, 但都未至於一食野就肚痛+肚屙。<br />\n但由8月中開始, 唔知係咪飲咗豆漿+山藥粉嘅影響, 即刻肚痛+屙, 已經即刻停咗(平時都無對豆漿敏感)...自此之後個肚就不定期地攪肚痛+肚屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係食完野, 基本上8成會肚痛+肚屙....唔知係咪因為食太多菜? 有去睇醫生但醫生都只係話可能係腸胃炎未好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 平日嘅飲食習俗係勁多菜少肉。但上網睇話&quot;高纖維的食物能促進腸道蠕動, 使腹瀉情況加重&quot;, 咁係咪代表要食少啲菜?<br />\n咁樣搞法好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無巴絲分享下飲食心得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61254dd70542a9e2e58c534446686a9859fd29e8","tid":2185343,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:02:24.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"dfd6fdfec62da71c1e3ce9cf125469f7c860a600","tid":2185343,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪SIBO<br />\n豆漿同山藥都多oligosaccharide餵啲菌食搞到你脹氣<br />\n可以試吓low fodmap先<br />\n再唔得就cut所有纖維"},{"pid":"67b8e249dc005e0176243ffc57a888cf1ce84580"